      • read

        public PskMessage read(CodecContext context,
                       InputStream inputStream)
                throws IOException
        インタフェースからコピーされた説明: Codec
        Read an object from the buffer according to the rules defined in the CodecContext.
        定義:
        read インタフェース内 Codec<PskMessage>
        パラメータ:
        context - An instance of CodecContext.
        inputStream - An instance of InputStream to read data from.
        戻り値:
        An instance of T as decoded from inputStream.
        例外:
        IOException - If anything goes wrong reading from the InputStream.

      • parsePrivateData

        public PskMessage parsePrivateData(byte[] data)
        Parse the private data portion of a PSK Message.

        This uses the standard read method but starts in the private headers state.

        パラメータ:
        data - The private data of a PSK message (headers and data separated by an empty line).
        戻り値:
        A new PSK Message with only private headers and data.

      • writePrivateData

        public byte[] writePrivateData(PskMessage message)
        Write the private headers and data of the message to a stream and return as a byte array.
        パラメータ:
        message - The decrypted PSK message
        戻り値:
        private headers and data encoded to bytes
